step_data.action: stop('Comparison of the Sceptre E195BD-SRR 19-Inch LED TV ($209.99) and Intel NUC Kit NUC6i7KYK Mini PC ($599.99):\\n\\nSceptre E195BD-SRR:\\n- 19-inch 720P LED TV (1366 x 768 resolution)\\n- Built-in DVD player\\n- HDMI and USB connectivity\\n- Weighs 5.6 pounds\\n- Energy Star certified\\n- Includes headphone jack and optical output\\n\\nIntel NUC Kit NUC6i7KYK:\\n- Mini PC with 6th Gen Intel Core i7-6770HQ processor\\n- Intel Iris Pro Graphics 580\\n- Supports up to 32GB DDR4 RAM\\n- Multiple USB 3.0 ports and Thunderbolt 3 technology\\n- Designed for gaming and intensive workloads\\n- Weighs 3.08 pounds\\n\\nThe NUC is a powerful computing device while the Sceptre is a basic display device with built-in DVD functionality.')
